150
00:11:50,172 --> 00:11:54,555
The different bars are different container sizes.

151
00:11:54,855 --> 00:11:57,497
Bedford in green there is a 64-gallon cart.

152
00:11:57,957 --> 00:12:02,040
The ones on the left are smaller, all the way down to just 33-gallon bags.

153
00:12:02,540 --> 00:12:06,002
And the ones on the right are up to 96-gallon carts of trash.

154
00:12:06,082 --> 00:12:06,783
So as you can see,

155
00:12:07,474 --> 00:12:16,563
Medford is kind of up on the higher end of Massachusetts communities in terms of how much trash is being disposed of.

156
